    <p id="intro">After growing up in San Diego, I have come by a few favorite places to eat and things to do. 
        <br>These may not be top picks on "things to do in San Diego" websites, but they are on my favorite list.
        <br> I hope you are able to enjoy some if not all of the activities and eateries listed.</p>
<h2 id="sectionTitle" class="sectionTitle">Food</h2>
